versus partnership model

00:37:32.880 --> 00:37:35.340 align:middle line:84%
and how that occurs
everywhere in our society,

00:37:35.340 --> 00:37:37.956 align:middle line:90%
between education and media.

00:37:37.956 --> 00:37:39.330 align:middle line:84%
And right now
